#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:155
msgid ""
"TVTC LMP is a large e-learning platform that allows universities and their "
"faculties to manage courses, course content, exams, assignments, online "
"learning with virtual classes, grading systems, and skill development. This "
"platform is one of my best pieces of work in terms of software engineering, "
"supporting 300,000 users, including over 20,000 students taking exams "
"simultaneously. This makes it one of the largest e-learning platforms in the "
"MENA region."
